kuda teji, busur terbaik,

241
00:15:02,679 --> 00:15:03,640
pakaian dan topi,

242
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,479
tapi dia langsung tak sukai mereka pun.

243
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:07,359
Dia takkan guna juga.

244
00:15:08,919 --> 00:15:09,679
Namun, kebelakangan ini,

245
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:12,159
saya baru dapati dia suka naga.

246
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:14,640
Naga?

247
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:16,520
Ya.

248
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:18,359
Naga ini,

249
00:15:18,559 --> 00:15:20,359
bukannya seperti singa dan harimau.

250
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:21,919
Jika dia suka haiwan begini,

251
00:15:22,039 --> 00:15:23,599
saya boleh tangkap untuk dia.

252
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:25,640
Biarpun saya tahu dia suka naga,

253
00:15:26,559 --> 00:15:28,440
saya tak boleh buat apa-apa
untuk menawan hatinya.

254
00:15:28,799 --> 00:15:29,559
Ya,

255
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:33,239
sebab naga terbang di langit.

256
00:15:37,159 --> 00:15:38,239
Saya dah ada akal.

257
00:15:43,799 --> 00:15:45,559
Bagus!

258
00:15:47,559 --> 00:15:49,760
Tahniah, tuanku.

259
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:52,200
Kita dah meraih kemenangan
dalam peperangan ini.

260
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,679
Jadi, Negara Dong Luo

261
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:56,760
akan hantar puteri mereka
yang paling cantik, Puteri Rui,

262
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,599
untuk menjalinkan hubungan diplomatik
menerusi perkahwinan dengan kita.

263
00:15:59,239 --> 00:16:01,719
Tahniah, tuanku.

264
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,640
Chenyue.

265
00:16:12,919 --> 00:16:14,520
Tengoklah apa yang saya bawa untuk awak.

266
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,200
Layang-layang naga.

267
00:16:34,799 --> 00:16:35,880
Awak pasti ingin tengok

268
00:16:36,239 --> 00:16:37,840
naga terbang di langit, betul?

269
00:16:39,159 --> 00:16:40,159
Bagaimana awak tahu tentang ini?

270
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,919
Sesetengah perkara

271
00:16:42,119 --> 00:16:43,080
tak perlu ditanya,

272
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,760
janji hati terikat.

273
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:45,760
Betul?

274
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:49,280
Hati terikat?

275
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:57,880
Saya lelaki dan lebih tua daripada awak.

276
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,599
Awak harus panggil saya Abang Zheng.

277
00:17:00,239 --> 00:17:01,520
Saya abang Qingqing.

278
00:17:02,039 --> 00:17:03,119
Saya Long Yuchi.

279
00:17:03,679 --> 00:17:04,800
Tak kira mana awak pergi,

280
00:17:05,239 --> 00:17:06,439
saya tetap dapat cari awak.

281
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:09,640
(Jangan-jangan Abang Zheng
sedang mengilat-ngilatkan bahawa)

282
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,359
(dialah Raja Naga?)

283
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:14,719
(Namun, kenapa saya rasa...)

284
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:15,760
Chenyue?

285
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:20,439
Jom, kita pergi main layang-layang.

286
00:17:21,479 --> 00:17:22,239
Jom.

287
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,680
Ambil itu.

288
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:26,920
Jom.

289
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:33,479
Ia dah terbang.

290
00:17:35,479 --> 00:17:37,400
Tekan benang ini ke bawah begini.

291
00:17:37,719 --> 00:17:38,800
Mari, awak cuba.

292
00:17:41,439 --> 00:17:42,599
Bukan.

293
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:44,160
Ke bawah.

294
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:45,199
Ke bawah.

295
00:17:45,199 --> 00:17:46,280
Betul, ke bawah.

296
00:17:47,439 --> 00:17:48,479
Betul.

297
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:49,760
Bagus.

298
00:17:51,599 --> 00:17:52,599
Betul.

299
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:56,000
Betul, tarik sedikit.

300
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:02,239
Tengok.

301
00:18:02,439 --> 00:18:03,280
Ia terbang semakin tinggi!

302
00:18:03,479 --> 00:18:04,280
Ya.

303
00:18:12,719 --> 00:18:13,560
Tuan muda!

304
00:18:16,760 --> 00:18:18,640
Chenyue, saya ada urusan rasmi
yang perlu diuruskan segera.

305
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:19,479
Saya pergi dahulu.

306
00:18:19,599 --> 00:18:20,719
-Saya akan pulang dengan cepat.
-Cepatlah pergi.

307
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:34,719
(Awak boleh dikira sebagai naga?)

308
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,400
Itu naga.

309
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:52,760
Mari sini.

310
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:53,439
Ya, panglima.

311
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:54,239
Pegang ini.

312
00:19:23,839 --> 00:19:25,000
Awaklah orangnya?

313
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:29,199
Kenapa sebaik saja Abang Zheng pergi,

314
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:30,560
naga muncul pula?

315
00:19:31,319 --> 00:19:32,560
Jangan-jangan dia nak
mengilat-ngilatkannya kepada saya?

316
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:34,719
Namun, kenapa awak
tak nak terus luahkannya?

317
00:19:36,959 --> 00:19:38,359
Awak malu?

318
00:19:39,479 --> 00:19:41,920
Tuan Raja Naga, muncullah!

319
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:43,680
Saya takkan ketawakan awak!

320
00:19:49,760 --> 00:19:51,959
Raja Naga kata dia takkan cemburu.

321
00:19:52,079 --> 00:19:53,040
Lihatlah.

322
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:57,119
Raja Naga tak boleh
bersama dengan Chenyue

323
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:59,839
dan hanya boleh lihat Chenyue
bergembira dengan orang lain.

324
00:20:00,760 --> 00:20:01,680
Lihatlah Raja Naga.

325
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:04,199
Jelas sekali, dia cemburu
terhadap naga palsu itu.

326
00:20:04,479 --> 00:20:05,760
Tengok cara dia terbang itu.

327
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,239
Raja Naga merupakan botol cuka,

328
00:20:08,439 --> 00:20:09,760
jag cuka, tong cuka.

329
00:20:21,319 --> 00:20:22,880
(Kenapa bunyi gelak
ketawa dalam otak saya)

330
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:25,160
(rasa-rasa kenal)

331
00:20:25,800 --> 00:20:27,040
(tapi asing juga?)

332
00:20:29,079 --> 00:20:30,400
(Siapa dia sebenarnya?)

333
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:33,560
Seronoknya.

334
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:44,520
Abang Zheng!

335
00:20:46,359 --> 00:20:47,199
Sini.

336
00:20:55,359 --> 00:20:56,520
Abang Yuchi.

337
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:00,520
Apa yang awak cakap ini?

338
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:01,959
Jangan malu, Raja Naga.

339
00:21:02,280 --> 00:21:03,560
Saya tahu awak Raja Naga.

340
00:21:05,359 --> 00:21:06,560
Apa Raja Long?

341
00:21:07,439 --> 00:21:09,400
Jangan-jangan awak berhubungan
dengan Raja Long yang memberontak itu?

342
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:12,599
(Saya dah salah faham.)

343
00:21:12,719 --> 00:21:13,920
Jangan cakap sembarangan kelak.

344
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:17,199
Habislah jika ia tersebar ke Fengdu.

345
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:18,719
Tak kira apa raja itu,

346
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:19,920
jangan ungkit lagi.

347
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,560
-Namun, Naga...
-Jangan ungkit lagi.

348
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:30,520
Tiada apa-apa lagi.

349
00:21:52,239 --> 00:21:53,199
(Saya pasti)

350
00:21:53,800 --> 00:21:55,239
(Raja Naga mesti ada di sisi saya.)

351
00:21:56,239 --> 00:21:57,199
(Siapa dia?)

352
00:21:59,079 --> 00:22:00,400
(Jika dia bukan Abang Zheng,)

353
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:02,839
(kenapa Abang Zheng hadiahi saya
layang-layang naga putih?)

354
00:22:04,359 --> 00:22:06,719
(Kenapa naga muncul
dan terbang di langit tadi?)

355
00:22:19,199 --> 00:22:21,920
Kawalan angkatan tentera Keluarga Feng
ketat dan susah hantar orang ke dalam.

356
00:22:22,079 --> 00:22:24,800
Tak begitu mudah
untuk kerjakan Feng Chenyue.

357
00:22:25,479 --> 00:22:27,400
Kita perlu merasuahi
pegawai kerajaan di Fengdu

358
00:22:28,239 --> 00:22:31,199
agar kita boleh ambil tindakan semasa
Feng Chenyue pulang ke Fengdu.

359
00:22:33,599 --> 00:22:36,199
Ayahanda dah hantar Rui pergi jalinkan
hubungan diplomatik melalui perkahwinan.

360
00:22:36,479 --> 00:22:37,560
Patik dah faham.

361
00:22:38,359 --> 00:22:39,760
Patik akan menemani puteri ketujuh

362
00:22:39,959 --> 00:22:41,160
untuk pergi ke Fengdu.

363
00:22:41,439 --> 00:22:42,839
Rui seorang pengecut.

364
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:45,239
Kali ini, saya akan suruh dia dengar
cakap awak dalam apa jua perkara pun.

365
00:22:45,479 --> 00:22:47,520
Patik pasti akan buat
Feng Chenyue pulang ke Fengdu

366
00:22:47,959 --> 00:22:49,079
lalu menyerang dia.

367
00:23:28,839 --> 00:23:30,640
Kota Fengdu sangat cantik.

368
00:23:34,839 --> 00:23:35,719
Selepas semuanya diuruskan,

369
00:23:35,839 --> 00:23:36,959
saya mesti keluar berjalan-jalan.

370
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:38,880
Mungkin saya dapat cari
makanan kampung halaman.

371
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:03,560
Baginda sediakan Astaka Xi Lai
yang sangat selesa

372
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:05,719
pada setiap musim khas untuk Gundik Rui.

373
00:24:05,959 --> 00:24:07,920
Baginda memang amat sayang Gundik Rui.

374
00:24:10,520 --> 00:24:11,599
Gundik Rui.

375
00:24:17,079 --> 00:24:18,040
Sida-sida Li.

376
00:24:18,599 --> 00:24:20,439
Sila terima hadiah kecil ini.

377
00:24:27,119 --> 00:24:28,000
Gundik Rui.

378
00:24:28,160 --> 00:24:29,599
Jika Gundik Rui
ada apa-apa pesanan kelak,

379
00:24:29,959 --> 00:24:30,880
sila datang cari patik.

380
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:32,560
Patik minta diri dahulu.

381
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:37,000
Kamu keluar juga.

382
00:24:43,119 --> 00:24:44,520
Akhirnya, mereka dah pergi.

383
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:46,719
Saya tak buat apa-apa
yang salah tadi, betul?

384
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:48,119
Tuan puteri buat dengan baik sekali.

385
00:24:49,199 --> 00:24:52,160
Jadi, apa yang perlu
saya buat seterusnya?

386
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:54,000
Berdasarkan peraturan istana,

387
00:24:54,239 --> 00:24:56,199
Gundik Rui patut banyak berhubung dengan

388
00:24:56,319 --> 00:24:57,319
permaisuri.

389
00:24:57,560 --> 00:24:59,479
Feng Chenyue akan datang ke Fengdu juga?

390
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,160
Jika kita mahu dia datang,

391
00:25:01,359 --> 00:25:02,520
dia pasti akan datang.

392
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:03,719
Kita mahu dia datang,

393
00:25:03,839 --> 00:25:05,040
dia pasti akan pulang?

394
00:25:07,319 --> 00:25:09,800
Tuan puteri mesti penat kerana
perjalanan jauh, sila berehat awal.

395
00:25:15,439 --> 00:25:16,599
Ini apa?

396
00:25:18,239 --> 00:25:19,400
Ini Kunci Kiub Ajaib.

397
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:21,119
Kunci Kiub Ajaib?

398
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,680
Menariknya.

399
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:37,560
Menitahkan Panglima Feng balik
ke Fengdu untuk terima ganjaran?

400
00:25:39,560 --> 00:25:41,040
Biarpun dia muda,

401
00:25:41,479 --> 00:25:42,880
dia mampu mengundurkan tentera Dong Luo.

402
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,079
Ia amat jarang didapati.

403
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:48,920
Tuanku.

404
00:25:50,199 --> 00:25:51,479
Bakat dia memang jarang dijumpai,

405
00:25:51,839 --> 00:25:53,319
patik juga kagum dengannya.

406
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:55,079
Namun, orang yang peroleh
pencapaian tinggi pada masa muda

407
00:25:55,520 --> 00:25:57,119
mestilah agak berlagak.

408
00:25:57,880 --> 00:26:00,199
Sekarang, hanya
angkatan tentera Keluarga Feng

409
00:26:00,560 --> 00:26:03,280
yang berada di kawasan sempadan
tak menghormati kerajaan.

410
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:06,839
Beta percaya Panglima Feng
bukan orang begini.

411
00:26:07,239 --> 00:26:09,319
Tuanku, panglima yang
ada di medan perang

412
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,959
tak semestinya akan
bertindak ikut perintah tuanku.

413
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:13,479
Pada pendapat patik,

414
00:26:13,959 --> 00:26:15,400
tuanku boleh guna peluang ini

415
00:26:15,719 --> 00:26:16,959
untuk mengetahui sama ada
angkatan tentera Keluarga Feng

416
00:26:17,199 --> 00:26:19,959
berlagak selepas meraih
kemenangan dalam peperangan

417
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:23,959
atau taat setia kepada tuanku.

418
00:26:27,359 --> 00:26:30,040
Panglima Feng Chenyue
menewaskan Negara Dong Luo.

419
00:26:30,239 --> 00:26:31,560
Baginda bertimbang rasa
terhadap panglima kegemarannya

420
00:26:31,719 --> 00:26:34,160
dan menitahkan Panglima Feng pulang
ke Fengdu dalam masa sepuluh hari

421
00:26:34,319 --> 00:26:37,479
untuk menerima ganjaran. Sekian.

422
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:41,439
Junjung kasih, tuanku.
Patik menjunjung titah.

423
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:48,319
Tahniah, Panglima Feng.

424
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,760
Namun, sepuluh hari bukan
masa yang panjang.

425
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:52,760
Panglima Feng, sila
buat persediaan segera.

426
00:26:53,239 --> 00:26:54,640
Jika masa tertangguh,

427
00:26:55,040 --> 00:26:56,359
ia dikirakan mengingkari titah.

428
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:57,319
Baik.

429
00:26:57,880 --> 00:27:00,079
Awak mesti penat daripada
perjalanan jauh. Pak Cik Zhao.

430
00:27:00,199 --> 00:27:00,839
Ya.

431
00:27:01,079 --> 00:27:02,680
Bawa sida-sida pergi mandi dan makan.

432
00:27:03,239 --> 00:27:04,199
Sida-sida, silakan.

433
00:27:14,319 --> 00:27:14,959
-Panglima.
-Cik Qingqing...

434
00:27:15,079 --> 00:27:16,719
Akhirnya, kita boleh pulang ke Fengdu.

435
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:18,520
Apa bagusnya Fengdu?

436
00:27:19,119 --> 00:27:21,160
Tempat ini bebas dan indah.

437
00:27:21,520 --> 00:27:23,040
Tentulah Fengdu bagus.

438
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:25,680
Chenyue, awak akan diganjari,

439
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:27,880
tapi awak hanya diberi masa
sepuluh hari untuk pulang ke Fengdu.

440
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:30,239
Jadual ini memang menyeksa awak.

441
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,920
Ia pasti bermasalah.

442
00:27:33,199 --> 00:27:34,199
Jangan risau.

443
00:27:34,959 --> 00:27:36,040
Bertindak

444
00:27:36,560 --> 00:27:38,040
ikut keadaan saja.

445
00:27:39,560 --> 00:27:43,280
(Kediaman Xu)

446
00:27:47,319 --> 00:27:50,079
Khabarnya, baginda dah panggil
panglima wanita, Feng Chenyue

447
00:27:50,239 --> 00:27:51,439
pulang ke Fengdu.

448
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,920
Feng Chenyue bagaikan
ratu di kawasan sempadan.

449
00:27:54,160 --> 00:27:56,479
Seratus ribu askar menuruti arahan dia.

450
00:27:57,520 --> 00:27:59,239
Dia memang begini berkemampuan?

451
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:02,000
Panglima Feng Huise dapat
anak perempuan pada usia tua.

452
00:28:02,199 --> 00:28:03,560
Seratus ribu angkatan
tentera Keluarga Feng

453
00:28:03,760 --> 00:28:05,400
menemani dia main saja.

454
00:28:07,680 --> 00:28:10,640
Sebagai seorang wanita,
dia pegang jawatan rasmi di Fengdu.

455
00:28:10,959 --> 00:28:13,079
Jadi, dia mesti faham peraturan Fengdu.

456
00:28:14,079 --> 00:28:15,800
Saya akan luangkan masa

457
00:28:16,119 --> 00:28:17,640
untuk mengajar dia.

458
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:47,719
Panglima.

459
00:28:48,199 --> 00:28:50,359
Awak melatih Teknik Pedang Xuan Tian.

460
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:52,439
Teknik pedang ini terkenal
dengan kelajuannya.

461
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,119
Dalam dunia ini,

462
00:28:54,560 --> 00:28:56,839
setahu saya, tak melebihi
tiga orang reti teknik pedang ini.

463
00:28:57,520 --> 00:29:00,079
Lagi sukarnya nak guna
teknik ini secara lancar.

464
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:01,920
Saya amat kagum.

465
00:29:02,319 --> 00:29:03,520
Terima kasih atas pujian panglima.

466
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:05,239
Mari berlawan dengan saya.

